{"tid":2112335,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊支那GAME公司，諗緊辭唔辭職","createTime":"2020-07-17T08:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T02:05:19.000Z","uid":198503,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5b0b9b87e22a7588f46a87fede68faf89f1b2890","tid":2112335,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"公司係紅底Game company，有藍有黃，黃嘅多，包括我自己<br />\nOFFICE又柒，個老細同某個成都嚟嘅同事成日睇支那嘢<br />\n前排示威又屌香港人唔知足，有自由重想點<br />\n<br />\n你哋喺youtube見到啲on 99遊戲廣告，基本上就係畫嗰類嚟呃鳩人玩<br />\n而呢啲Marketing唔到artist話事，<br />\n而係公司唔識art嘅marketing post同事去做(臺灣同事長住香港）<br />\n<br />\n呢份工我返左差唔多一年，當然間公司係中資，電腦用殘體Windows，用殘體正版Adobe，<br />\n上年HD grad到而家都就嚟有19.5k，因為係中資，<br />\n比起其他本土公司叫價高好多，多兩三四千蚊<br />\n<br />\n最遲有時ot到八點幾，原本返八到五，前排直頭過份到星期六都要WFH，<br />\n有幾個同事頂唔順支那working culture都走埋<br />\n之後WFH啲圖直頭喺屋企畫晒佢，<br />\n但係workload大好撚好撚多，又無啦啦要做埋份約唔包嘅3D<br />\n但係我開始好迷失，開始唔知點解去做呢份工，<br />\n呢份工做嘅嘢其實我唔係真係鍾意，我真係睇人工份上先捱成年<br />\n<br />\n個senior成日有咩唔想做就俾我做<br />\n畫game圖，有character design，environment design，之後要我學埋3d，基本上學到係周身刀無把利<br />\n畫完對自己成長無幫助，個senior都話：你入嚟唔係學嘢，係做嘢，唔好成日諗住想畫咩就畫咩，夾返其他artist嘅風格係你唯一可以做嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n我以前讀書做design，炒散，啲同事好人事好多<br />\n大家都玩得好埋<br />\n而家大家都係各有各做，喺公司幾乎無咩chemistry<br />\n有支那同事成日講<br />\n<br />\n但係出到去我諗我都搵唔到份咁嘅價錢嘅工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明人生好多妥協，但係我已經唔知自己想點"},{"pid":"056213993519c0da6a410f36d0c572896e4a4dbc","tid":2112335,"uid":72228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:41:39.000Z","msg":"樓主自己諗諗<br />\n香港地做game好難搵到好價錢<br />\n自己諗諗轉行仲好"},{"pid":"1706ea509714666177d94ba0db2418b34f54156b","tid":2112335,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"056213993519c0da6a410f36d0c572896e4a4dbc","tid":2112335,"uid":72228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:41:39.000Z","msg":"樓主自己諗諗<br />\n香港地做game好難搵到好價錢<br />\n自己諗諗轉行仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"可能係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6514b08e111d450e2be2cb6f61b2b2b54a9371","tid":2112335,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:47:03.000Z","msg":"得個hd 一係搵書讀仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbc395c37b0b3a6d6f1026bf2379feea197f8d2","tid":2112335,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c6514b08e111d450e2be2cb6f61b2b2b54a9371","tid":2112335,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:47:03.000Z","msg":"得個hd 一係搵書讀仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:52:50.000Z","msg":"有諗過，但係我本身有ADHD，除左語文，數學比同輩差好多倍，讀書唔係易事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f002af820194c00cdedbf4a9f94d6d8a72f617","tid":2112335,"uid":55493,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T09:01:24.000Z","msg":"梗係照做之後hea做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n貢獻仲大過做黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757e456943671ef3767979f33b7e7a2170ce2dee","tid":2112335,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T09:03:04.000Z","msg":"手遊定pc??"},{"pid":"d8032c45c55360a6e6cc04f3251a695a33d6f4cd","tid":2112335,"uid":19337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T09:06:05.000Z","msg":"將大陸錢轉化做香港人錢<br />\n點解要辭職"},{"pid":"2f8d7165aa03810a3bf39449ee830fdf452c5920","tid":2112335,"uid":6696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T09:07:40.000Z","msg":"做game 咁低人工？<br />\n19.5已經高